      "text": "こ、こころちゃん、突然どうしたの……？\nそれに妹って……私の方が年上なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kokoro-chan‚ what's going on…?\nAnd you say imouto… I'm older than you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333334287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.4333336194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事で子役の子と共演することになったんですけど\n小さい子との絡み方がイマイチよく分からなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm working with a child actorss‚ and\nI'm not really sure how to interact with little kids…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4333336194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.1000002861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
