      "text": "普通に、いつも通りのこころちゃんで\nいいんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't it fine to be just normal‚\nKokoro-chan as usual?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.8333338737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
