      "text": "莉央さんに相談してみたんですけど\nそしたらすっごーく、怖いことを言ってきたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I tried talking to Rio-san about it‚\nbut she said something reallyー scary",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4333350182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
