      "bgName": "tokyosmrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.3000016849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_04-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "「普段、私達にしているような悪戯はしないことね\n子役にそれしたら、パワハラになるわよ」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said 'First of all‚ you shouldn't tease us like you do‚\nIf you do that to child actor‚ it's workplace bullying'…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3000016849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
