      "text": "うわぁ～～ん、嫌です～～～\n子役と絡むの怖いです～、パワハラしたくないです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaah~~‚ no~~~\nI'm scared of working with child actor~‚ I don't want to be a teaser~",
        "id": ""
