      "text": "すみれちゃん。簡単に言いますけど……\nこころにそれが出来ると思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ It's easy to say…\nDo you think Kokoro can do that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3333286604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosmrroom-01-night.webp",
